<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2944939>
    dc:description "FIGURES 156–165. Diagnostic characters to Apotrechae n. group. 156–160. Bianigryllacris n. gen. 156. Habitus of B. parvospinus n. comb. (Draw from Guo and Shi, 2012). 157–160. B. trilobus (draw from Bian et al., 2014). 157. Frons. 158. Male terminalia in dorsal view. 159. Male subgenital. 160. Ovipositor. 161–163. Apotrechus illawarra (draw from Rentz & John, 1990). 161. Frons. 162. Abdomen tip in dorsal view. 163. Male subgenital plate. 164. Ovipositor. 165. Frons of Apterolarnaca quadrimaculata (Bian et al., 2016)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2944939/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

